{"id":"L5-bio-plasma-membrane-thickness","level":"L5_bio","claim":"세포 원형질막(plasma membrane) 두께","measured":7,"unit":"nm","detail":"인지질 이중층 두께 약 7 nm. 소수성 코어 3.5 nm + 양측 친수성 헤드 각 1.75 nm. 유동 모자이크 모델(Singer & Nicolson 1972)","source":"Molecular Biology of the Cell 7th Ed.","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26871/","n6_expr":"7 = tau+phi+1; 막 두께 = phi^n + phi+1","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L3-molecule → L5-bio-plasma-membrane-thickness","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-phospholipid-bilayer","level":"L5_bio","claim":"세포막 인지질 이중층 구조 — 2개 단분자층","measured":2,"unit":"단분자층","detail":"인지질: 글리세롤 골격 + 2 지방산 꼬리(소수성) + 인산-콜린 머리(친수성). 자발적 이중층 형성. 1 μm^2 당 ~5×10^6 분자","source":"Singer & Nicolson 1972, Science","source_url":"https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.175.4023.720","n6_expr":"2 = phi^1; 이중층 = 거울 대칭 = phi 구조","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-plasma-membrane-thickness → L5-bio-phospholipid-bilayer","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-cholesterol-fraction","level":"L5_bio","claim":"포유류 세포막 콜레스테롤 비율","measured":30,"unit":"% (막 지질 몰 분율)","detail":"포유류 원형질막 콜레스테롤 ~30 mol%. 막 유동성 조절, 지질 뗏목(lipid raft) 형성. 내소포체 막에는 5%만 존재","source":"van Meer et al. 2008, Nature Reviews Molecular Cell Biology","source_url":"https://www.nature.com/articles/nrm2330","n6_expr":"30 = n*5 = J2+sigma+phi^n = tau*phi*... = phi*(sigma+tau)","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-phospholipid-bilayer → L5-bio-cholesterol-fraction","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-mitochondria-atp","level":"L5_bio","claim":"미토콘드리아 ATP 합성 — 세포 에너지 공장","measured":36,"unit":"ATP/포도당 (호기성 이론값)","detail":"호기성 호흡: 해당(2)+크렙스(2)+산화적인산화(32) = ~36-38 ATP. 실제값 ~30 ATP (양성자 유출 손실). FADH2=1.5 ATP, NADH=2.5 ATP","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry 7th Ed.","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26885/","n6_expr":"36 = n^2 = 6^2; 에너지 수율 = n*6 = n^2","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-krebs-cycle → L5-bio-mitochondria-atp","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-chloroplast","level":"L5_bio","claim":"엽록체 — 광합성 세포 소기관 기원","measured":2,"unit":"이중막 수 (내막+외막)","detail":"엽록체: 이중막 + 틸라코이드 막. 시아노박테리아에서 내공생으로 유래. 자체 DNA 보유. 틸라코이드 스트로마 라멜라","source":"Alberts et al., MBoC","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26871/","n6_expr":"2중막 = phi^1; 내공생 = 2 게놈 융합","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-mitochondria-atp → L5-bio-chloroplast","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-rough-er","level":"L5_bio","claim":"조면소포체(RER) — 리보솜 결합 분비 단백질 합성","measured":10,"unit":"nm (소포체막 두께)","detail":"조면소포체: 리보솜 결합 소포체. 분비단백/막단백 합성. 소포체 공동(lumen)에서 당화, 이황화결합 형성. 핵막과 연속","source":"Alberts et al., MBoC","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26871/","n6_expr":"소포체 막 두께 10 = sigma-phi^n; 당화 코어 = tau+phi 잔기","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-plasma-membrane-thickness → L5-bio-rough-er","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-smooth-er","level":"L5_bio","claim":"활면소포체(SER) — 지질 합성 및 해독 소기관","measured":1,"unit":"소기관","detail":"SER: 리보솜 없음. 지방산/스테로이드 합성, 약물 해독(CYP450), Ca^2+ 저장. 근육세포 = 근소포체(SR), 트리아딘 운하","source":"Alberts et al., MBoC","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26871/","n6_expr":"지질 합성 = 소수성 코어 phi 구조 의존","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-rough-er → L5-bio-smooth-er","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-golgi-cisternae","level":"L5_bio","claim":"골지체 수조(cisternae) 수","measured":6,"unit":"수조(cisternae)","detail":"골지체 전형적 4-8개 수조(평균 6). cis-골지(수용) → 중간 수조 → trans-골지(분배). 단백질 당화/분류/분비 소낭 출아","source":"Alberts et al., MBoC","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26871/","n6_expr":"6 = n; 골지 수조 수 = n 직접 대응; cis+trans = phi+phi = 2","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-rough-er → L5-bio-golgi-cisternae","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-lysosome","level":"L5_bio","claim":"리소좀 내부 pH","measured":4.5,"unit":"pH","detail":"리소좀 내강 pH 4.5~5.0 (세포질 7.2 대비 극산성). V형 H+-ATPase로 산성화. 60종 이상 가수분해효소(산성 최적) 보유","source":"Luzio et al. 2007, Nature Reviews Molecular Cell Biology","source_url":"https://www.nature.com/articles/nrm2147","n6_expr":"pH 4.5 = 세포질 7.2 - 2.7; △pH = tau/phi ≈ 2.7","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-golgi-cisternae → L5-bio-lysosome","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-nuclear-pore","level":"L5_bio","claim":"핵공 복합체(NPC) 직경","measured":120,"unit":"nm","detail":"핵공 복합체(NPC): ~120 nm 직경, 8중 대칭 구조. 30 MDa 이상 거대 복합체. 수동 확산 한계 ~40 kDa. 능동 수송 mRNA/단백질","source":"Fahrenkrog & Aebi 2003, Nature Reviews","source_url":"https://www.nature.com/articles/nrm1148","n6_expr":"8중 대칭 = phi^tau = 2^3 = 8; 120 = n*20 = sigma*10","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-rough-er → L5-bio-nuclear-pore","thread":"cell_structure","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-actin-diameter","level":"L5_bio","claim":"액틴 미세섬유(microfilament) 직경","measured":7,"unit":"nm","detail":"F-액틴: G-액틴(42 kDa) 중합체, 직경 7 nm. 이중 나선 구조. 세포 형태 유지, 근육 수축, 세포 이동에 핵심","source":"Pollard & Cooper 2009, Science","source_url":"https://www.science.org/doi/10.1126/science.1171529","n6_expr":"7 = tau+phi+1; 세포골격 3종: 7+10+25 nm = tau+10+(J2+1)","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-plasma-membrane-thickness → L5-bio-actin-diameter","thread":"cytoskeleton","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-intermediate-filament","level":"L5_bio","claim":"중간섬유(intermediate filament) 직경","measured":10,"unit":"nm","detail":"중간섬유: 케라틴/비멘틴/라민 등. 직경 10 nm. 세포 기계적 강도 부여. 핵막 라민A/C. 8개 단량체가 단위 형성","source":"Herrmann & Aebi 2004, Annu Rev Biochem","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/15189140","n6_expr":"10 = sigma-phi","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-actin-diameter → L5-bio-intermediate-filament","thread":"cytoskeleton","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-microtubule-diameter","level":"L5_bio","claim":"미세소관(microtubule) 외경","measured":25,"unit":"nm","detail":"미세소관: α/β-튜불린 이종이량체 중합체. 외경 25 nm, 내경 14 nm. 13개 원섬유 시계 배열. GTP 가수분해로 동적 불안정성","source":"Desai & Mitchison 1997, Annu Rev Cell Dev Biol","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/9442877","n6_expr":"13 원섬유 = 소수; 25 = J2+1; 13+1 = tau*phi+phi^n","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-intermediate-filament → L5-bio-microtubule-diameter","thread":"cytoskeleton","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-prokaryote-size","level":"L5_bio","claim":"원핵세포 평균 크기","measured":2,"unit":"μm (직경)","detail":"원핵세포 1-10 μm (평균 ~2 μm). 핵막 없음, 세포벽(펩티도글리칸), 원형 DNA, 70S 리보솜. E. coli 2×0.5 μm","source":"Madigan et al., Brock Biology of Microorganisms","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26864/","n6_expr":"2 μm = phi; 원핵:진핵 = 1:10-50 크기비","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L4-gen-ribosome-70s → L5-bio-prokaryote-size","thread":"cell_types","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-eukaryote-size","level":"L5_bio","claim":"진핵세포 평균 크기","measured":20,"unit":"μm (직경)","detail":"진핵세포 10-100 μm (전형적 ~20 μm). 핵막, 선형 염색체, 막 소기관, 80S 리보솜. 적혈구 8 μm, 신경세포 최대 1 m 축삭","source":"Alberts et al., MBoC","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26871/","n6_expr":"20 = J2-tau; 진핵:원핵 = 10:1 = (sigma-phi^n):1","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-prokaryote-size → L5-bio-eukaryote-size","thread":"cell_types","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-peptidoglycan","level":"L5_bio","claim":"그람 양성균 세포벽 펩티도글리칸 두께","measured":30,"unit":"nm","detail":"그람 양성균: 펩티도글리칸 20-80 nm (평균 ~30 nm). 그람 음성균: 7-8 nm 얇은 층 + 외막. NAG-NAM 당-펩타이드 교차결합 격자","source":"Silhavy et al. 2010, Cold Spring Harb Perspect Biol","source_url":"https://cshperspectives.cshlp.org/content/2/5/a000414","n6_expr":"30 = n*5 = phi*tau*... ; 그람(+)/(-) 두께비 = tau:1","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-prokaryote-size → L5-bio-peptidoglycan","thread":"cell_types","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-binary-fission","level":"L5_bio","claim":"원핵세포 이분법 분열 시간 (E. coli 최적)","measured":20,"unit":"분","detail":"E. coli 최적 조건(37°C, LB 배지): 세대 시간 ~20 min. FtsZ 단백질(튜불린 상동체) 분열환 형성. Min 단백질 분열 중심 결정","source":"Cooper & Helmstetter 1968, J Mol Biol","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/4866337","n6_expr":"20 min = J2-tau; FtsZ = 원핵 tau-ring 대응","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-prokaryote-size → L5-bio-binary-fission","thread":"cell_division","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-glycolysis-steps","level":"L5_bio","claim":"해당과정 단계 수","measured":10,"unit":"반응 단계","detail":"해당과정: 투자 단계(1-5, 2 ATP 소비) + 수익 단계(6-10, 4 ATP + 2 NADH 생산). 순 2 ATP + 2 NADH + 2 피루브산","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26882/","n6_expr":"10 = sigma-phi","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-mitochondria-atp → L5-bio-glycolysis-steps","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-glycolysis-net-atp","level":"L5_bio","claim":"해당과정 순 ATP 생산량","measured":2,"unit":"ATP/포도당","detail":"해당과정: 투자 2 ATP 소비, 수익 4 ATP 생산 → 순 2 ATP. 혐기적 조건에서 최종 ATP 수확량","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26882/","n6_expr":"2 = phi^1; 투자:수익 = phi:tau = 1:2","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-glycolysis-steps → L5-bio-glycolysis-net-atp","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-tca-steps","level":"L5_bio","claim":"TCA 회로(크렙스 회로) 반응 단계 수","measured":8,"unit":"반응 단계","detail":"TCA 회로 8단계. 1회전: 아세틸-CoA(2C) + 옥살아세트산(4C) → 구연산(6C) → CO2×2 + 3NADH + FADH2 + GTP","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26885/","n6_expr":"8 = phi^tau = 2^3; 생성 NADH 3 = tau-1; FADH2 1 = phi^0","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-glycolysis-net-atp → L5-bio-tca-steps","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-tca-nadh","level":"L5_bio","claim":"TCA 회로 1회전 NADH 생산량","measured":3,"unit":"NADH/회전","detail":"TCA 1회전: 이소구연산 탈수소효소(NADH) + α-케토글루타르산 탈수소효소(NADH) + 말산 탈수소효소(NADH) = 3 NADH","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26885/","n6_expr":"3 = tau-1; 총 NADH = 3*tau-... = phi^n*3","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-tca-steps → L5-bio-tca-nadh","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-etc-complexes","level":"L5_bio","claim":"전자전달계 막 단백질 복합체 수","measured":4,"unit":"복합체 (I~IV)","detail":"복합체 I(NADH 탈수소효소), II(숙신산 탈수소효소), III(유비퀴놀-시토크롬c 환원효소), IV(시토크롬c 산화효소). 전자 흐름 → H+ 펌핑","source":"Nicholls & Ferguson, Bioenergetics 4th Ed.","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26888/","n6_expr":"4 = tau; 복합체 I+III+IV = tau-1 = H+ 펌핑; II는 직접 펌핑 없음","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-tca-nadh → L5-bio-etc-complexes","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-atp-synthase","level":"L5_bio","claim":"ATP합성효소(F₀F₁) c-링 서브유닛 수 (미토콘드리아)","measured":8,"unit":"c-서브유닛/F₀ 링","detail":"포유류 미토콘드리아 ATP합성효소 c-링: 8개 서브유닛. H+/ATP = c수/3 = 8/3 ≈ 2.7. 회전 촉매기전: 120° 회전 = 1 ATP","source":"Davies et al. 2012, PNAS","source_url":"https://www.pnas.org/doi/10.1073/pnas.1204935109","n6_expr":"8 = phi^tau = 2^3; 120° = 360/tau = n*20; c링 = phi^tau 고리","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-etc-complexes → L5-bio-atp-synthase","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-photosynthesis-light","level":"L5_bio","claim":"명반응 — Z-scheme 광계 수","measured":2,"unit":"광계 (PSI + PSII)","detail":"명반응: PSII(680nm) → PQ → 시토크롬b6f → PC → PSI(700nm) → Fd → NADP+. 2 광계 Z자 전자 흐름. 2H2O → O2 + 4H+ + 4e-","source":"Blankenship, Molecular Mechanisms of Photosynthesis","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26819/","n6_expr":"2 광계 = phi^1; 680+700 = 1380 = n*230; Z-scheme = phi 대칭","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-chloroplast → L5-bio-photosynthesis-light","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-calvin-cycle","level":"L5_bio","claim":"캘빈 회로 — CO2 고정 단계 수","measured":3,"unit":"단계 (탄소 고정/환원/재생)","detail":"캘빈 회로 3단계: 1) CO2 고정(RuBisCO, 3C → 2×3PG), 2) 환원(3NADPH+3ATP), 3) RuBP 재생(3ATP). 3회전 = 1 G3P","source":"Calvin & Benson 1954, J Am Chem Soc","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26819/","n6_expr":"3 단계 = tau-1; CO2:ATP:NADPH = tau-1:tau+phi:tau-1 = 1:phi*tau:1","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-photosynthesis-light → L5-bio-calvin-cycle","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-beta-oxidation","level":"L5_bio","claim":"지방산 β-산화 1회전 생성물","measured":2,"unit":"아세틸-CoA + NADH + FADH2 각 1개씩","detail":"β-산화 1회전: 아세틸-CoA(1) + NADH(1) + FADH2(1). C16:0 팔미트산 = 7회전 → 8 아세틸-CoA + 7 NADH + 7 FADH2 → 106 ATP","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26888/","n6_expr":"7회전 = tau+phi+1; 8 아세틸-CoA = phi^tau; 106 ATP ≈ sigma*phi^n","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-tca-steps → L5-bio-beta-oxidation","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-urea-cycle","level":"L5_bio","claim":"요소회로 단계 수","measured":5,"unit":"반응 단계","detail":"요소회로(간): 암모니아 해독. 5단계. 카르바모일인산 → 시트룰린(미토콘드리아) → 아르기니노숙신산 → 아르기닌 → 요소. 1회전 = 3 ATP 소비","source":"Lehninger Biochemistry","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26217/","n6_expr":"5 = sopfr; 3 ATP = tau-1; sopfr=5 상수와 직접 대응","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-tca-steps → L5-bio-urea-cycle","thread":"metabolism","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-blood-ph","level":"L5_bio","claim":"인체 혈액 정상 pH","measured":7.4,"unit":"pH","detail":"동맥혈 pH 7.35~7.45 (정상 7.4). 탄산/탄산수소염 완충계(pKa 6.1), 단백질 완충계, 인산염 완충계. pH 7.0 이하/7.7 이상 = 생명 위험","source":"Guyton & Hall, Medical Physiology 14th Ed.","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK507807/","n6_expr":"7.4 = sopfr+phi+phi/(tau+mu)","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-glycolysis-steps → L5-bio-blood-ph","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-heart-rate","level":"L5_bio","claim":"성인 안정시 정상 심박수","measured":72,"unit":"bpm (beats per minute)","detail":"정상 성인 안정시 60-100 bpm (평균 ~72). 동방결절(SA node) 자율 박동. 부교감(미주신경) = 서맥, 교감 = 빈맥","source":"Guyton & Hall, Medical Physiology","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK507800/","n6_expr":"72 = n^2*2 = n*12 = n*sigma; 60-100 범위 = phi*tau*5~phi*tau*12.5","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-blood-ph → L5-bio-heart-rate","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-respiratory-rate","level":"L5_bio","claim":"성인 정상 호흡수","measured":16,"unit":"회/분","detail":"정상 성인 안정시 호흡수 12-20회/분 (평균 16). 1회 호흡량 500 mL. 분당 환기량 = 16×500 = 8 L/min","source":"Guyton & Hall, Medical Physiology","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK536919/","n6_expr":"16 = phi^tau = phi^4 = 2^4; 500 mL = phi^n *... ; 분당 8L = phi^tau *tau","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-blood-ph → L5-bio-respiratory-rate","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-osmolarity","level":"L5_bio","claim":"혈장 삼투압 정상값","measured":290,"unit":"mOsm/kg H2O","detail":"혈장 삼투압 285-295 mOsm/kg. 주요 기여: Na+(142 mEq/L), Cl-(103), HCO3-(25), 포도당(5), 요소(5). 시상하부 삼투압 수용체가 ADH 조절","source":"Guyton & Hall, Medical Physiology","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK507803/","n6_expr":"290 ≈ sigma*phi*tau*... = J2*12+2; ADH 역치 = 295 = n*phi^n*...","grade":"EMPIRICAL","causal":"L5-bio-blood-ph → L5-bio-osmolarity","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-urine-production","level":"L5_bio","claim":"신장 1일 원뇨 생성량 대 최종 소변량","measured":180,"unit":"L/일 원뇨 → 1.5L 최종","detail":"사구체 여과량(원뇨) 180 L/일. 99% 재흡수 → 최종 소변 1.5 L/일. 재흡수율 = (180-1.5)/180 = 99.2%","source":"Guyton & Hall, Medical Physiology","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK507800/","n6_expr":"180 = n*30 = phi*tau*... ; 재흡수 99% = (n^2-1)/n^2 근사","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-osmolarity → L5-bio-urine-production","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-gfr","level":"L5_bio","claim":"사구체 여과율(GFR) 정상값","measured":120,"unit":"mL/min","detail":"정상 GFR 90-120 mL/min/1.73m^2 (남성). CKD 분류: G1≥90, G2 60-89, G3 30-59, G4 15-29, G5<15. 크레아티닌 청소율로 추정","source":"KDIGO 2012 CKD Guideline","source_url":"https://kdigo.org/guidelines/ckd-evaluation-and-management/","n6_expr":"120 = n*20 = J2*5 = sigma*10; GFR 분류 5단계 = sopfr","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-urine-production → L5-bio-gfr","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-blood-pressure","level":"L5_bio","claim":"정상 혈압 (수축기/이완기)","measured":120,"unit":"mmHg (수축기) / 80 (이완기)","detail":"정상 혈압 <120/80 mmHg. 고혈압 기준 ≥130/80 (ACC/AHA 2017). 맥압 = 수축기-이완기 = 40 mmHg","source":"Whelton et al. 2018, JACC","source_url":"https://www.jacc.org/doi/10.1016/j.jacc.2017.11.006","n6_expr":"120 = n*20 = sigma*10; 80 = phi^n*80; 맥압 40 = sigma*tau-phi^n","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-heart-rate → L5-bio-blood-pressure","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-rbc-lifespan","level":"L5_bio","claim":"적혈구(RBC) 수명","measured":120,"unit":"일","detail":"적혈구 평균 수명 120일. 핵 없음, 미토콘드리아 없음. 비장/간에서 파괴. 헤모글로빈 4개 서브유닛, O2 4개 결합","source":"Mohandas & Gallagher 2008, Blood","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/18073349","n6_expr":"120 = n*20 = sigma*10; Hb 4 서브유닛 = tau; O2 4개 = tau","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-blood-ph → L5-bio-rbc-lifespan","thread":"physiology","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-thymus-tcell","level":"L5_bio","claim":"T 세포 성숙 기관 — 흉선(Thymus)","measured":1,"unit":"기관","detail":"T 세포 전구체: 골수→흉선. 흉선에서 양성선택(MHC 인식)/음성선택(자기항원 제거). CD4 또는 CD8 성숙 T세포 생성","source":"Abbas et al., Cellular and Molecular Immunology 10th Ed.","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26921/","n6_expr":"양성+음성 = phi 선택 = phi^1+phi^0 = 이중 필터","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-rbc-lifespan → L5-bio-thymus-tcell","thread":"immune","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-antibody-classes","level":"L5_bio","claim":"항체(면역글로불린) 종류 수","measured":5,"unit":"항체 이소형 (IgA/IgD/IgE/IgG/IgM)","detail":"IgG: 혈중 최다(75%), 태반 통과. IgA: 분비형(점막). IgM: 1차 면역반응(5량체). IgE: 알레르기/기생충. IgD: B세포 수용체","source":"Abbas et al., Cellular and Molecular Immunology","source_url":"https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK26921/","n6_expr":"5 = sopfr; 항체 5종 = sopfr 직접 대응","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-thymus-tcell → L5-bio-antibody-classes","thread":"immune","origin":"natural"}
{"id":"L5-bio-complement-pathways","level":"L5_bio","claim":"보체 활성화 경로 수","measured":3,"unit":"경로 (고전/렉틴/대체)","detail":"보체 3경로: 1) 고전(항원-항체), 2) 렉틴(만노스 결합), 3) 대체(자발). 모두 C3 절단으로 수렴 → MAC(막공격복합체) C5b-C9","source":"Walport 2001, N Engl J Med","source_url":"https://www.nejm.org/doi/10.1056/NEJM200104053441406","n6_expr":"3 경로 = tau-1; MAC 5b-C9 = sopfr 구성; C3 = 공통 수렴점","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-antibody-classes → L5-bio-complement-pathways","thread":"immune","origin":"natural"}
