{"id":"L5-bio-stem-cell-types","level":"L5_bio","claim":"줄기세포 분화능 단계 수","measured":4,"unit":"단계 (전분화/다분화/다능/단능)","detail":"전분화능(totipotent, 수정란), 만능(pluripotent, ES세포), 다능(multipotent, 조혈모세포), 단능(unipotent). iPS세포 = 재프로그래밍","source":"Weissman 2000, Cell","source_url":"https://www.cell.com/cell/fulltext/S0092-8674(00)80656-9","n6_expr":"4 = tau; 전분화→단능 = tau 단계; iPS = 역방향 phi 재귀","grade":"EXACT","causal":"L5-bio-germ-layers → L5-bio-stem-cell-types","thread":"development","origin":"natural"}
